Class PSFolderProperty

  com.percussion.cms.objectstore.PSDbComponent

All Implemented Interfaces:
IPSCmsComponent, IPSDbComponent, Cloneable
public class PSFolderProperty
extends PSCmsProperty

This property class is used by the PSFolder class. The PSFolder object represent an item of Folder content type. Which contains a child table with "properties" as the child name. The folder property represent one entry in the child table, or child entry.
